      "title": "Quick Start",
      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": [
        "1. Drop your converted SCAIL-2.safetensors in models/diffusion_models/\n2. Drop Wan2.1_VAE.pth in models/vae/\n3. Drop the T5 .pth in models/text_encoders/\n4. Drop the CLIP vision .pth in models/clip_vision/\n5. Copy the umt5-xxl/ and xlm-roberta-large/ HF tokenizer dirs into models/scail2/tokenizers/\n6. Set quick_preview=true on the sampler for fast prompt iteration; toggle off for full long-video runs.\n7. Run the Debug Inputs node first — if ambiguous pixels >2%, fix your masks before sampling."
      ]
